:"現實冇咁易<br />\n你星批入花頭轉，佢另一邊螺絲都會跟住轉<br />\n姐係好似以前果種得一邊士巴拿咁<br />\n而且搵士巴拿夾緊個半圓/水泡餅冇用<br />\n佢入邊照轉到，要直接卡佢螺絲果邊<br />\n等螺絲轉唔到就可以扭星批"},{"pid":"52783ee5bc5b3ceaf79a6b38202387e2aff6b3ab","tid":2030373,"uid":182596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:52:39.000Z","msg":"鐵馬係用嚟推㗎！"},{"pid":"552cba8d755a9789519976014acb27d759d3c152","tid":2030373,"uid":101307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:54:02.000Z","msg":"召喚連登工程師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dae50060f698f609815cee71969043dfecd4c0","tid":2030373,"uid":322398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"最好<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔好</span>拆哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a891bf5a8c0c5e9c77c3aa063768478f58ac0da1","tid":2030373,"uid":182596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3dae50060f698f609815cee71969043dfecd4c0","tid":2030373,"uid":322398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"最好<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔好</span>拆哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:03:17.000Z","msg":"留27<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fab85bfff9e15a851566153d6328228545453e","tid":2030373,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"多數支那野<br />\n淘寶應該好多專家"},{"pid":"4bc02fc855cbf306f8bbbb6680f2bac121186c0d","tid":2030373,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"想推番上黎先<br />\n24果日啲花頭上哂石屎，個難度高左好多<br />\n有冇巴打知其他方法"},{"pid":"040356dad56a8c46a6df702167d0e15d4f985613","tid":2030373,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"24/5無鐵欄都一街rb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=